OL,7,F"We can confirm that we have started
OL,8,Fan investigation into West Midlands
OL,9,FPolice's response to a number of
OL,10,Falleged incidents reported to them
OL,11,Fbefore a fatal collision in
OL,12,FHandsworth, Birmingham, on February
OL,13,F18".
