OL,3,CInvestigation into police's handling
OL,4,Cof crash suspect 'known' before fatal
OL,5,Csmash
OL,7,F"Our investigation follows West
OL,8,FMidlands Police's mandatory referral
OL,9,Fof a complaint about how police dealt
OL,10,Fwith calls reporting incidents at a
OL,11,Fhealth unit on February 17".J"We have
OL,12,Fbeen told that a man involved in those
OL,13,Fincidents was arrested in connection
OL,14,Fwith a traffic collision in Soho Road
OL,15,Fthe following day, in which a man
OL,16,Fdied. We understand that another
OL,17,Fperson was also seriously injured when
OL,18,Fa car struck a number of parked
OL,19,Fvehicles.JIOPC regional director
OL,20,FDerrick Campbell added:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
