OL,5,Csmash
OL,7,F"My sympathies are with the family of
OL,8,Fthe man who died and everyone else
OL,9,Faffected by this terrible incident.
OL,10,FOur investigation, which is at a very
OL,11,Fearly stage, will consider the prior
OL,12,Fpolice contact and whether
OL,13,Fopportunities were missed to prevent
OL,14,Fwhat happened the following day."
