OL,7,FMr Hanif from Handsworth was sitting
OL,8,Fwith his best friend . He ran
OL,9,FCheckpoint Tyres in and was due to act
OL,10,Fas best man at a friend's wedding
OL,11,Flater that week.JAbbas Hanif, 24,
OL,12,Fdescribed his older brother as the
OL,13,F"best, kind, polite and caring". His
OL,14,Fgrieving wife said in a poignant
OL,15,Ftribute: "Hizar was the most driven
OL,16,Fand passionate person I knew.J"He went
OL,17,Fabove and beyond for his family and
OL,18,Ffriends, everyone who knew him loved
OL,19,Fhim. His smile will be greatly missed,
